<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EduHub Activation Code</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a, #10b981);
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        background: #e1e2cd;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      .logo {
        font-size: 34px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #16a34a;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #111827;
      }

      .description {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .code-box {
        margin: 30px auto;
        background-color: #f3f4f6;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 18px 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 14px;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
        box-shadow: inset 0 0 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        color: #111827;
      }

      .note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 40px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #4b5563;
      }

      .footer a {
        color: #10b981;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .signoff {
        margin-top: 50px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: #1f2937;
      }

      .team {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #16a34a;
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">EduHub</div>
      <div class="title">Hi <%= user.name %></div>
      <h3>Let’s Get You Activated</h3>
      <p class="description">
        We use this simple activation code so you can start learning right away
        — no complex password required.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-weight: 600">Your activation code is:</p>
      <div class="code-box"><%= activationCode %></div>
      <div class="note">This code is valid for the next 5 minutes only.</div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Have questions or trouble logging in?</p>
        <p>
          Just reply to this email or contact
          <a href="mailto:support@eduhub.com">support@eduhub.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="signoff">
        All the best, <br />
        <span class="team">The EduHub Team</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
